entries.feedback: End-of-session guide is helpful. Could automate session file creation with a CLI tool or template generator.
Output Flywheel v1.0 pipeline works great! Successfully generated README, build log, and social post. Would benefit from automated git commit extraction to populate git_commits array in session JSON.
Session file creation helper CLI would streamline end-of-session workflow - automatically generate UUID, timestamp, and basic structure based on session type.
